               <h3>Follow the instructions to run the application</h3>
          <div class="info3">
        <h2>Mentor Mode:</h2>
        <p>1.Choose the video file from your local system using the choose button</p>
        <p>2.Click the play button</p>
        <p>3.Click the pause button whenever you find a mistake</p>
        <p>4.Give the Feedback using the textarea provided and then click the save button once</p>
        <p>5.Then click the play button again to continue the video</p>
        <p>6.Repeat this procedure until you reach end of the video or you finish giving the feedback </p>
        <p>7.Back button is also provided in-case if you want to listen the video again</p>
        <p>8.When you press the back button video will be moved 5 seconds backward and it continues again from there</p>
        <p>9.After finishing the feedback press the "End of the Feedback" button</p>
        <p>10.You will be re-directed to Thank you page where you can either review your feedback or exit from the application by pressing the appropriate buttons</p>
        <p>11.You can exit from the application after viewing your feedback by pressing the "Exit" buttons</p>
        <p>12.End of the Mentor Mode</p>
          </div>
       
        <div class="info4">
        <h2>Student Mode:</h2>
        <p>1.Choose the same video file from your local system for which the mentor has given you feedback using the choose button</p>
        <p>2.Then Press the "Load the Feedback button"</p>
        <p>3.In the text area provided at the right hand side you will get all the timings(TimeStamps List) where you have given the feedback</p>
        <p>4.Choose the same  feedback file again from your local system</p>
        <p>5.Click to play the video from the player itself</p>
        <p>6.Make use of Previous and Next comments buttons to get the comments in the text area provided above them</p>
        <p>7.Also Note that the timings get display in the text box respectively according to the button pressed for Next and Previous Comments</p>
        <p>8.After finishing your viewing feedback close the window <p>
        <p>9.That will be end of the student mode</p>
          </div>
